      <h2>Getting here by plane</h2>
      <p>The airport of the city of Bremen lies some 45 km east of Oldenburg. There is a bus shuttle service that runs between airport and the city of Oldenburg, early registration for this service is recommended though.</p>

      <h2 class="lowerh2">Getting here by train/bus</h2>
      <p>The station of the city of Oldenburg is 3 km away from the OFFIS building. In case you are pressed for time, we recommend taking a taxi. Otherwise, take bus #308 from "Hauptbahnhof/ZOB" (station/central bus terminal) to "Johann-Justus-Weg" (line's final destination) and get off the bus at "Industriestra&szlig;e".</p>

      <h2 class="lowerh2">Getting here by car</h2>
      <p>Take Highway A28, exit "OL-Haarentor" and keep driving towards the city centre. Having driven for some 700m, turn left at the traffic lights. After another kilometer turn left again right behind a grocery store; the street sign should say "Industriestra&szlig;e" now. After another 200m take the second left ("Escherweg"). There is a parking lot for guests right behind the OFFIS building.
